    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 是一款数学记忆挑战游戏，共有 13 个阶段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A.1 经典投币模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏的规则很简单。如果你失去所有健康，游戏就结束了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决大量数学问题，到达游戏终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/383b2f32053b6ef5743e6b1060dbeebb.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/383b2f32053b6ef5743e6b1060dbeebb.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/383b2f32053b6ef5743e6b1060dbeebb.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B.根式系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以选择下一阶段出现的公式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/91b71160dc55afcf5b80dc4b4c03ac42.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/91b71160dc55afcf5b80dc4b4c03ac42.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/91b71160dc55afcf5b80dc4b4c03ac42.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >C. 商店系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次正确解题都会获得金币，金币可用于在完成一个阶段后出现的各类商店中购买有用的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/9ee9659f3445ccc5cfdc0923ac7c7e93.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/9ee9659f3445ccc5cfdc0923ac7c7e93.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/9ee9659f3445ccc5cfdc0923ac7c7e93.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D. 支持练习模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持练习模式，可自由练习 32 个公式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/31623eb7bd569397294c4ce330647970.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/31623eb7bd569397294c4ce330647970.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/31623eb7bd569397294c4ce330647970.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E. 3 个难度级别</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/6901fc35c2e092699a5e2916c2c7c647.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/6901fc35c2e092699a5e2916c2c7c647.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=